Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:06.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,This special video has been provided to all of you by Shounen Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:13.51,Signs,,0,0,0,,When you watch TV, please brighten the room and don't sit too close to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:23.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Shounen Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promised to lend you my manga the other day, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, there are only 24 volumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only twenty four?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you can return it to me any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, when you want to give them back, return it one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Carrying all of it is pretty heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You could have brought one by one too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great detectives also like to read manga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading can help you relax sometimes, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dream Station Bug, "Kamen Yaiba III: The Three Magician"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, the game takes place in the magical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the old witch appear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go play it at Conan's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? My house again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your house is the secret base of the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A secret base?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know about your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the old witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:41.59,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Koizumi Akako
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This ball is floating in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a real magic ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My family has passed this magic ball from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It will answers any question I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, magical ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything you want to tell the boy with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At the place where you will meet a tiger, a vulture and a giant frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Be ready to find a way out of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vulture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A giant frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case, you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sh-She disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really is the old...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about the prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:44.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Other than the fortune telling, there is something else that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mouri Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, we have clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you want me to protect the treasure sword mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this announced from Kaitou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:18.07,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mine Shizuka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:18.07,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mine Sayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the famous detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I'm sure you can defeat Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"Tonight at 8:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I will enter your noble home to retrieve your treasure sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kaitou Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, can't let down my guard for even a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I, Mouri Kogoro, will take on this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not only protecting your treasure sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch Kaitou Kid at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We are in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eh? Come to think of it, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where have I seen them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.11,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Mine family house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we talking about Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiddo-schmiddo, your help would be completely useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Retired Person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will protect the sword ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, don't come crying to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was dealing with these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These men? Aren't these policemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sayaka, who are these people behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Detective Mouri Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and his daughter Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And also the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They might can help protect the sword from Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, just a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This grandma is harder to deal with than Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secure the perimeter of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go inside, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:42.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Kurogane Yaiba
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, who is this Kanchou Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just a lowly thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yaiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will give him what he deserves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Yaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because you don't look like Kamen Yaiba at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're completely wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not Kamen Yaiba, I am Kurogane Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Kamen Yaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where the kids went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably playing around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Mine Raizou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Mine Raizou, the head of this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my daughter Ran and our house guest, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that my wife and my daughter invited you here on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My family and I are all students of kendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, when Kid shows up, he will understand that the advantage will be on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, please rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kid is arrested, we can have a little something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a very big yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can even play hide and seek here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, gero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the vulture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you shouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Kid? Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vulture...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giant frog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Kagetora, Shonosuke, Gerozaimon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're scaring the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagetora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shonosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gerozaimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, they're just pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gave us a fright for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This place is from a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But what's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And what is this strange feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, those little kids with their false alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Y-Yo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kurogane Kenjuurou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me? I am Kurogane Kenjuurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where do you keep the treasure sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Uncle can't protect it if he doesn't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:31.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Paikal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I drank it before, I returned to my original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:40.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said, we don't need a detective's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma, do you often drink that liqueur?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I use this liqueur for various herbal treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I have it a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But only a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, not that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a secret medicine that has been passed down in our family from generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can cure any disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may not taste very good, but it will help with the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink it all in one gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body is burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe something is about to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "one more"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only lost sight of you for a moment, and look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Children should not drink liqueur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tell you, it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be like my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ko-go-rou; go = five
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Kogorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ken-juu-rou; juu = ten
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm Kenjuurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Juugo-rou; juugo = fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And together we are Juugorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid should appear in 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone take your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mansion is very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this is going to be even more worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me, Kaitou Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where could that sword be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hurts, gero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scream for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, gero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this a monster's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I should get my work done quickly and leave this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kaitou Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin your pretty face, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't bother you, I would like to know where the sword is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the kendo dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They have a dojo here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Throw your bamboo sword away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful flower is more suitable for beautiful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, madam, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of you, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kid! How dare you fool my wife and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the most charming person I have met this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, your charm won't work on my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't have a chance with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right, that medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's possible with this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It starting, it starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi Ran, long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Split into two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A mustache? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kid! He disguised himself as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he? Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kid is over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mine Dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did they hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you give me that treasure sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Kanchou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ka-Kanchou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kaitou, you pinhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're very skilled, Kanchou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kaitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the sword, pinhead{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! I have to do something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe if I drink a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did he run to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem, Inspector Nakamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm Hattori... Hattori!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:44.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jirokichi, the Japanese Robin Hood who was a theif in 1800's Japan\N(nicknamed Nezumi Kozo, "Rat Boy") who stole from the rich and gave to the poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must say, you are great. You remind me of that rat boy thief, Jirokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not some chivalrous thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long, pinhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get him, Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:13.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this strange feeling bothering me since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}By the way, those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Kurogane Yaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show him something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a wonderful fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, could it be, that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the treasure sword that Kid tried to steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that Yaiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} took care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, Yaiba did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You not introduced yourself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am Kudou Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous high school detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, I've been bothered by a strange feeling since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I finally understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} isn't wearing her usual head scarf, instead she's wearing a ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 10-yen bald spot on Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s hair should be on the right side,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today it's on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} doesn't have freckles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two locks of hair he always has dangling in front have become three.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her bangs are parted differently than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on get up, they will come for you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See what happens when you read manga late into the night? You can't get up on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get ready, I need to clear the breakfast table.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:57.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just a dream...
